description: Taoiseach (Irish PM) Leo Varadkar says hairdressers, churches, sport teams can all resume activity from 29 June.
title: Covid-19: ROI Hairdressers and sport back from 29 June
title_page: Covid-19: ROI Hairdressers and sport back from 29 June - BBC News
maintext: "But we all need to stay careful, it will not be as it was before the start of the pandemic and for now sports will take place with very limited numbers of spectators.
